quoridor.model

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • quoridor.model.Player
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AIPlayer, HumanPlayer

    public abstract class Player
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable
    Player abstract class. Represents a player (Human or AI) that can play against another player (Human or AI). This class has abstract methods that defines the basic player actions.
    See Also:
